  "prompt": "How do I contact Handy customer service?",
  "response": "There are several ways to contact Handy customer service:\n\n*   **Through the Handy App or Website:** This is generally the best and fastest method.\n\n    *   **Handy App:** Open the app, tap the \"Help\" or \"Support\" section (usually in the menu or settings), and look for options like \"Contact Us,\" \"Chat,\" or a \"Help Center.\"\n    *   **Handy Website:** Go to the Handy website (handy.com). Look for a \"Help\" or \"Support\" link in the header or footer.\n\n*   **Phone:** While Handy encourages using the app or website for support, you might find a phone number through online searches. Be aware that wait times may be longer.\n\n*   **Social Media:** You can try reaching out to Handy through their social media channels (like Twitter or Facebook). This might be a quicker way to get a response.",
